    public class NotificationResourceImpl
extends SwSynchronizationResourceImpl
implements NotificationResource
    An implementation of the model object 'Notification Resource'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Occurence
    • Mechanism
    • Occurence Count Elements
    • Mask Elements
    • Flush Services
    • Signal Services
    • Wait Services
    • Clear Services
